raph","children":[{"text":"**7 new files created:**\n```\nai-research/index.mdx                  ← overview + stats + CardGroup nav\nai-research/marketing/overview.mdx\nai-research/tech-builds/overview.mdx\nai-research/business/overview.mdx\nai-research/personal/overview.mdx\nai-research/ecommerce/overview.mdx\nai-research/content/overview.mdx\n```"}]}]
